item.title: Another refference for K.Y. Lvl 2
item.content:encoded: The R00t version of K.Y. is also a reference to BT from .hack//SIGN with it being highly implied that BT and Bear had a relationship in the past, K.Y. lvl 2's picture looking somewhat like BT and the fact that both characters have only two letter abriviations for their names.
